CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 26, 1955, pg. A4, reads: "Hat Model - Charming Gussie Ellison made a hit with the patrons of Delta Sigma Theta's fashion show at the William Penn Hotel recently, when she modeled a number of custom made hats created by Ruth Lee. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Gussie Ellison modeling dark short sleeved dress, long dark gloves with button at wrist, and light colored headband, posed near mural of West End - North Side Bridge, Pittsburgh, for Delta Sigma Theta fashion show, William Penn Hotel
